{
  "stem": "12491.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it got infected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It got swollen, and so that my thigh was like a ball and to be operated on to remove the pus, the infection.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And since the German doctor would not operate on me, I was transported to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The colonel provided a horse, a buggy [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] covered with-- with straw what I was laying on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the soldier who was driving me to the-- into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was taken into the hospital in ghetto, the operation was performed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the operation, that was-- the situation in ghetto and in ghetto hospital was very crude.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The operation was performed, and during the operation I woke up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- my wrists were tied to the operating table, and I sit up and looked at all the blood on my thigh and I started saying, what are you doing to me?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the doctor, Doctor Lefkovich, who operated on me, just moved off and hit me in my face with his elbow, and I was-- they put the mask on me, and I was down.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eventually they finished the operation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wound up in the-- in hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was already March, 1943.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "March 1943 was the time when the ghetto was liquidated, and the concentration camp in Plaszow was initiated, and they actually moved the people-- excuse me-- moved the people from ghetto to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the process, they killed many in the ghetto before they moved them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, of course, all the people who were in the hospital died by injecting or taking poison.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was in that hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since I had contacts-- people were-- people were two and sometimes three to a bed because there was no room.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But since I had contacts, I had one bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
